                },
                {
                    "text": " ordered pizza and it should be here in ten minutes"
                }
            ],
            "tips": "Often used with present perfect ('has already left') or past perfect ('had already finished'). Position: before main verb ('She has already gone') or at end of sentence ('She's gone already')."
        },
